---
layout: post
title: 性学入门 李银河
---
It gives a thorough introduction to sexuality, by first going through the history of sex study and extracting the main ideas and contributions of important researchers. Then talk about the relationship between sex and biology, physiology, society, law, culture, politics and philosophy.
You can find the note for this book [here](https://www.notion.so/35cc872073a54eddb6e1b576b69e177f).
